{"id":42963,"title":"[ALPPS in case of massive liver metastases].","abstract":"It was presented the first experience of ALPPS technique using in treatment of massive liver metastases in the Urals. The technique allows to carry out surgical treatment without danger of development of post-operative liver failure. Also it permits to complete treatment during one hospitalization without stretching the therapeutic process in time. ","date":"2014-05-12","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24816383","annotations":[{"name":"Psychotherapy","weight":0.765521,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychotherapy"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.701843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.55757,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Metastasis","weight":0.318828,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metastasis"},{"name":"Liver failure","weight":0.23144,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liver_failure"},{"name":"Liver","weight":0.186848,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liver"},{"name":"Ural Mountains","weight":0.0290048,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ural_Mountains"},{"name":"Stretching","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stretching"},{"name":"Hospitalization","weight":0.0162839,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospitalization"},{"name":"Developmental biology","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Developmental_biology"}]}
